{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/DESPAIR1.png?t=1737021912\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/Test372-2024.12.13-19.27.31.22.gif?t=1737021912\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;If the universe is infinite, what could be waiting for you in its depths?&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Desperate Travelers</strong> is a world of <strong>advanced</strong> technology and<strong> interplanetary</strong> trade, where <strong>strange</strong> and <strong>terrifying</strong> events are unfolding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare your own <strong>space cruiser</strong>, enhancing its <strong>characteristics</strong> and <strong>design</strong> to suit your preferences. With your <strong>customized ship</strong>, you\u2019ll <strong>venture</strong> into<strong> uncharted territories</strong> filled with<strong> laboratories</strong>,<strong> catacombs,</strong> and <strong>testing grounds</strong>, all brimming with <strong>cunning traps</strong> and <strong>deadly enemies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/DESPAIR2.png?t=1737021912\" />A vast array of <strong>biological</strong> and <strong>mechanical</strong> <strong>foes</strong> will relentlessly <strong>pursue you</strong>, using every means possible to prevent you from <strong>claiming</strong> valuable <strong>resources</strong>. Besides these<strong> terrifying monsters</strong>, you\u2019ll also face numerous <strong>traps</strong> scattered across <strong>procedurally generated </strong>locations, as well as various <strong>natural disasters</strong>, from <strong>acid floods</strong> to <strong>meteor storms</strong>. Those few who manage to escape with their treasures onboard will have the option to sell their goods on the black market or in official stores, where danger might also lurk around every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/2gif-ez.gif?t=1737021912\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/gamefeatures.png?t=1737021912\" />  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Shuttle Vulnerability</strong>: Your shuttle can be destroyed\u2014make sure it doesn't happen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3D Voice Chat and Sound</strong>: Experience immersive audio with 3D voice chat and environmental sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Procedurally Generated Maps</strong>: No two maps are alike, ensuring a unique experience every time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Player Customization</strong>: Choose your body and accessories, then your corpse will not be confused with anyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Prepare the shuttle for flight, gather a team of brave astronauts and go on a thrilling journey through hostile space!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2946190/extras/4gif-ez.gif?t=1737021912\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"NO ONE IS SCARIER THAN HUMAN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2946190/5108f3e5aeb2946a2e8cbfc9fa0325ba3ce2ddd2.jpg"},{"name":"A bad feeling","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2946190/efdd73dab71e9787298180fc5df82a71f62064a1.jpg"},{"name":"DeadMan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2946190/88d148478f9c0b3d6f3fdc5cceff1c61d8fd9d3e.jpg"},{"name":" There are many of them","path"